## ğŸŒŸ About **Naan Mudhalvan Scheme**

The **Naan Mudhalvan Scheme** is a **skill development and career guidance program** launched by the **Government of Tamil Nadu**.
The main aim of this scheme is to **improve employability** and **future readiness** of students studying in **schools and colleges** across **Tamil Nadu**.

