## ğŸ“ Exam-Ready Short Answer (5 lines)

The Naan Mudhalvan Scheme is a skill development initiative launched by the Government of Tamil Nadu. It aims to provide students with industry-relevant skills and career guidance. The scheme benefits school and college students across Tamil Nadu. It offers free training in technical and soft skills. The program helps improve employability and future career opportunities.

